<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Stay Feedback Request</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #333;
        }
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 30px auto 0;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 0;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 2px solid #000000;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
            background-color: #D4AF37;
            color: #FDF6E3;
        }
        .header img {
            max-width: 150px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 25px;
            color: #0D0D0D;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .content h1 {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #333333;
        }
        .content p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #555555;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 15px 0;
            background-color: #D4AF37;
            color: #FDF6E3;
            font-size: 12px;
            margin-top: 0;
        }
        .footer img {
            max-width: 40px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .footer p {
            margin: 5px 0 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <h2>Thank You for Trusting Us with Your Cat!</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <h1>Your Cat's Stay Has Come to an End!</h1>
            <p>Hello {{user}},</p>
            <p>We hope your cat had a great stay with us and that the daily updates and care from our team met your expectations. As your catâ€™s visit concludes, we would love to hear about your experience.</p>
            <p>Would you mind taking a moment to share your thoughts with us? Your feedback helps us improve our services and ensure that every cat gets the best care possible.</p>
            <p>Please click the link below to leave a review:</p>
            <p><a href="{{reviewLink}}">Leave a Review</a></p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <img src="cid:logoApp" alt="Logo" />
            <p>&copy; 2025 The Fancy Box. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>Contact: +1112223331 | thefancyboxinc@gmail.com</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
